Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣在這裡貼上網點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後小祐 用自動鉛筆在這裡畫上頁碼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及給頭髮上色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長野原同學 會畫漫畫吶！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 哪有 不算什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前呀 還背著大家偷偷的畫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了吧 都是很久遠的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 前段時間投了次稿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄回來的原稿裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放了一封寫著「期待您的再次投稿」的信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是就覺得偷偷畫好像也有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們一定是覺得你很有才華！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微讓我看看麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃可以不用看的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.10,0:03:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去吹吹風…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？ 用我陪你麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家是來幫長野原同學弄原稿的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 名乃也真是夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 糟糕了 已經到這個時間了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這下可不能糊里糊塗的了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名乃回來之前 我們一口氣加快進度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟明天是投稿截止日期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解瞭解！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有很會畫的一面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就給你搞定喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員戰鬥開始～～！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼快就開始偷懶喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼 我稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.05,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\move(878,207,887,194)}要\N是\N做\N一\N匹\N太\N過\N的\N烈\N馬\N的\N話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.05,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\move(171,318,144,315)}我\N可\N要\N打\N你\N了\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.05,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\move(491,581,478,602,22,2524)}我\N說\N…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.92,0:04:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可要打你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說麻衣 你畫了什麼啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空也上人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\an8}空也（903-972）：平安時代中期僧侶，天台宗空也派的祖師。\N人稱阿彌陀聖、市聖、市上人等。民間也有評價稱其為淨土教的先驅者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是那個問題哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼擅自畫上去了呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為背景的空白在哭泣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說神馬！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之快把那裡塗上白色！！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡只有網點就可以了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它亂七八糟的都是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是我這輩子覺得最痛的一次了哦 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈… 趕快給頭髮上色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那——個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我我我我我我我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個… 誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個… ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒——！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫錯了的話 或者有什麼失誤的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之要馬上說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之不趕快修正的話！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 完成啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再擅自亂畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(879,208)}要\N是\N做\N一\N匹\N太\N過\N的\N烈\N馬\N的\N話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs33\frz35.158\pos(149,277)}墓\N地\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.99,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(479,584)}我\N說\N…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.53,0:05:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.08,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs48\frz35.158\pos(203,267)\c&H656363&}墓\N地\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓… 地哦！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你個笨蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是代官山的高級宮殿啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 畫上去 是不行的吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼擅自亂畫呢！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那裡有空間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棘手——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 算了… 總之好好給我擦掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只擦掉就夠了啊！！ 只擦掉哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫了一個很帥的出來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說畫了一個很帥的出來了 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像麼！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的給她也是火上澆油！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次好好擦掉了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 亂做多餘的事 可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(879,208)}要\N是\N做\N一\N匹\N太\N過\N的\N烈\N馬\N的\N話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs33\frz35.158\pos(149,277)}墓\N地\N哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.35,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs27\frz35.158\pos(479,584)}我\N說\N…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擦掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我把你擦掉嗎！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要擅自做這種事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個漫畫不怎麼有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把話說的太狠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會給你一張新的稿紙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那張紙上畫上同樣的網格線…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有網格線哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs90\c&H000000&\bord0\shad4\4c&HFCFCFC&\frz270\b1\pos(865,300)}Helvitica
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs90\c&H000000&\bord0\shad4\4c&HFCFCFC&\frz270\b1\pos(777,435)}Standard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收…收拾不了——
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是像與不像的問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 是誰啊！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的給她看也是火上澆油哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…真的只有網格線吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 有一個老爺爺和老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爺爺去上山砍柴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是從桃子裡出來的 二號生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣… 你去… 看書吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這… 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺越著急就越糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了… 不好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊… 怎麼辦哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你能做到麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能畫出來麼 麻衣！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能做出…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 誒！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個也非常激烈的厲害！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是… 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激烈的 越來越遠啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧… 回到那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對身邊的一切還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼東西都覺得很新鮮的 那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 說出來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將原原本本的自己！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬分抱歉啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您重新畫一張！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有稿紙了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 走廊裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笹原！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(652,493)\c&H0A0A0A&\shad0\bord0\K100}隻{\K100}言{\K100}片{\K100}語
加一句「死小鬼」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 拿不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒什麼含義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長野原前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 來這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒沒沒沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me  too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒 倒也… 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個… 實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明離大賽越來越近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻很難集中精神練習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長野原前輩高中的時候有遇到過這種事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺防具沉的要命之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒在聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,椎茸三昧這本漫畫 真是奇怪吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這傢伙除了劍道以外都 完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 什麼什麼？ 有趣的事麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不用了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長野原前輩你不也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快要參加全日本大賽了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道場也不來 美星她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 本來是要去買東西的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你煎餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼呢 在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才啊 長野原前輩來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？ 明天都是全日本大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧？ 明天麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說些什麼了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這個丟給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好紅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好紅吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:26.37,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,360)\fad(400,0)}菠\N蘿\N包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord1\blur2\c&H181818&\frz21.551\move(603,294,602,282)}菠蘿包
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\shad0\bord1\blur2\c&H181818&\frz21.551\move(712,531,722,558)}食用期限在麵包的背面標明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HD6A6FE&\pos(622,498)}與愛有關的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 美緒 來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心裡想著偶爾也要換一個形象 就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合適麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很小祐風…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.37,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\fscx95\bord2\pos(150,570)}雪\N飄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.37,TEXT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial\fs21\bord2\pos(212,570)}flsnow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那～ 我來找了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士 在哪裡啦～？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生 發～現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,僥倖這種東西可真可怕啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種小孩子的遊戲 我一般是不摻合的吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.08,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 偶爾也要跟你們一起玩玩啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕快繼續哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦誒 小鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底藏哪了啊 這小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的話可絕對不會被發現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼的話 可能藏到家外面了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.76,0:15:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定意外的就這樣一輩子都找不到了吶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是自己做的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為什麼出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話不就不是捉迷藏了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 我以為你們已經找不到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.57,0:16:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擤——
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擤… 鼻涕了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要洗的衣物不是又多了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我做鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來玩 下一把吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.68,0:16:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 博士給你洗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會變得亂糟糟的 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不會變得亂糟糟的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不 肯定會亂七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 沒關係的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.78,0:16:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\bord0\shad4\4c&HF4F2F1&\c&H96D291&}P{\c&H06BDE9&}y{\c&H0E009B&}o{\c&H92F052&}n{\c&H6F54E8&}是{\c&H7EA1AD&}這{\c&H7C1EA2&}個{\c&H5D4542&}樣{\c&H33FF6C&}子{\2c&H964CAE&\c&H974DAE&}的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 你說了什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你妹啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 來幫我我當然很高興了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄翻墨水的是小祐你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為已經沒有稿紙了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有辦法跟小祐你說去買的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 你說什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 到底我們誰去買…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囂張你妹啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把墨水弄翻的小祐你幹的你進去買啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多事情沒做完呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果是該小祐去買東西的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又說了什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說… 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.51,0:18:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來像幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰管你啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢進去的話 文具店要關門了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼現在突然問啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟實際年齡一樣啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿鞋的時候你說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好冷哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,揮淚斬馬謖哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要頑抗到什麼時候啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且今天一點也不冷啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 那也算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後 結果買回來的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你買的是稿紙啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要開這種玩笑了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說完這話 你拿出來的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 謝了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進退維谷啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你想讓我怎樣啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我那麼說了 你又說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我吧風信子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風信子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豈止是無聊啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風信子是從哪出來的啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那樣我也相信你了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信你會好好把稿紙買回來！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信那是一個太冷的笑話！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟你說快把稿紙拿出來結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼了！！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美緒 把頭腦風信子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風信子！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該把頭腦冷靜下來的是誰啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：風信子{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（ヒヤシンス）{\r\fs36}和冷靜{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（ひやす）{\r\fs36}音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不是不是 就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰該風信子啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是我又問了一遍啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問你「實際上是買了吧」！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果 你說什麼了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原諒人家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風信子哪去了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說 風信子怎麼著都隨便啦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稿紙啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果 你拿出來的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對對對 這個這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 用淫靡的文筆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來寫一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個蠢貨！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要前言不答後語到什麼程度才肯罷休啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底想要幹什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真實不一定是總是正確的對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小祐辦不成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就拜託名乃去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她說去買稿紙什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入迷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛像被釘住了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是喜極而泣啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法所以拜託麻衣去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣 可以幫我去買麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs27\bord0\shad0\c&H455D66&\frz31.216\pos(740,424)\frx44\fry14}我\N回\N去\N了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去了啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲都沒吱就回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣都按麻衣的步調來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣的步調 就是我行我素啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}譯註：麻衣的步調{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（まいのペース）{\r\fs30}與我行我素{\fnＤＦブラッシュＲＤW7\fs30}（マイペース）{\r\fs30}音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 看著那個紙條的小祐！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還記得你說什麼了麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是神的惡作劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是惡魔的 陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔的陷阱啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從你們幾個來的時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就已經是惡魔的陷阱了哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說了那些後 小祐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想聽你的解釋呢！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個 超級大傻瓜！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是不是 就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說還是花生米都沒有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花生米混蛋！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直說「就是說」「就是說」什麼的！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原諒你了 風信子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:06.89,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\blur3}あの素晴らしい愛をもう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:06.89,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\blur3}讓那何等美妙的愛情再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:29.21,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}命かけてと　誓った日から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:29.21,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}從立下賭上生命 的誓言的那一刻開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:38.76,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}素敵な思い出　残してきたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.50,0:22:38.76,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}明明還留下 那絕佳的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:47.73,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あの時　同じ花を見て　美しいと言った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.84,0:22:47.73,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}那個時候 看到同一朵花 都會說好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:58.94,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ふたりの　心と心が　今はもう通わない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:58.94,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}如今我二人 心與心之間 竟無法相通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:08.25,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}あの素晴らしい愛をもう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:08.25,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}讓那何等美妙的愛情再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:20.72,EDJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)\blur3}あの素晴らしい愛をもう一度

Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.00,0:23:20.72,EDCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1000)\blur3}讓那何等美妙的愛情再一次

Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是助你走向夢想的擺渡人 漫畫稿紙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.93,0:23:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在現在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛 堂堂正正的朝著描繪夢想的海報發射
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一話日常是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.59,0:23:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十一話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有送上門來的哦！